840
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:12,310
The hidden mark reacts to water.

841
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:15,150
Everyone, examine each other now.

842
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:16,800
Oh...

843
00:42:18,670 --> 00:42:20,000
- Nothing.
- Nothing on me either.

844
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,480
There's nothing.

845
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:32,710
What's on your chest?

846
00:42:35,900 --> 00:42:38,020
(Wang Heng)

847
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:41,400
Merely a stain

848
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,840
I accidentally got.

849
00:42:43,070 --> 00:42:43,910
Jiang Zhan!

